{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2>下载安装iterm2和ohmyzsh</h2>\n<p>过程略</p>\n<h2>iterm2主题</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">preferences</code>-><code class=\"language-text\">Profiles</code>-><code class=\"language-text\">Colors</code>中<code class=\"language-text\">color presets</code>选择<code class=\"language-text\">Solarized Dark</code></p>\n<h2>ohmyzsh字体</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/powerline/fonts\">fonts github链接</a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># clone</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">git</span> clone https://github.com/powerline/fonts.git --depth<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>1\n<span class=\"token comment\"># install</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">cd</span> fonts\n./install.sh\n<span class=\"token comment\"># clean-up a bit</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">cd</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">..</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">rm</span> -rf fonts</code></pre></div>\n<p>iterm2 <code class=\"language-text\">preferences</code>-><code class=\"language-text\">Profiles</code>-><code class=\"language-text\">Text</code>中勾选<code class=\"language-text\">Use a different font for non-ASCII text</code></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Font</code>和<code class=\"language-text\">non-ASCII Font</code>字体选择<code class=\"language-text\">14pt Meslo LG M Regular for Powerline</code></p>\n<h2>ohmyzsh主题</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">vi</span> ./.zshrc</code></pre></div>\n<h3>配置主题</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">ZSH_THEME=&quot;agnoster&quot;</code></pre></div>\n<h3>隐藏user@hostname</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">prompt_context(){}</code></pre></div>\n<h2>效果</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/2618447/6316862/70f58fb6-ba03-11e4-82c9-c083bf9a6574.png\"></p>","frontmatter":{"date":"July 09, 2018","path":"/blog/2018-07-09","title":"终端iterm2+ohmyzsh主题配置"}}},"pageContext":{}}